+Sharing Cart
+============
+
+version 3.2, release 1 - 2017.02.01
+
+The "master" branch is no longer compatible with Moodle 2.2 or earlier.
+
+* Moodle 2.2 => "MOODLE_22_STABLE" branch
+* Moodle 1.9 => "MOODLE_19_STABLE" branch
+
+Change Log
+----------
